==Weapons==
[[File:Gilded scimitar equipped.png|thumb|100px|A player wielding a [[gilded scimitar]].]]
'''Gilded weapons''' can be obtained as very rare rewards by completing [[Clue scroll (hard)|hard]], [[Clue scroll (elite)|elite]] and [[Clue scroll (master)|master]] [[Treasure Trails]]. However, the [[gilded spade]], [[gilded scimitar|scimitar]], [[gilded axe|axe]] and [[gilded pickaxe|pickaxe]] are only available from elite and master Treasure Trails.

All require level 40 [[Attack]] to equip and are statistically equivalent to their [[rune equipment]] counterparts.

